Ranger Help for: survey
=======================

SYNTAX:      survey (or: id)
USAGE:       Any terrain.
SLOT COST:   1
BASE SP:     2

SUMMARY:
Surveys the terrain you are standing in, identifying all terrain
types present and displaying them with color codes. Also reports
whether you are in your primary terrain, secondary terrain, or
claimed warden range, and shows the domain name.

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: terrains, setprime, setsecond, check
